Yeah, so my car broke down

48:39.150 --> 48:40.500
and now I'm being driven by

48:40.500 --> 48:43.025
the lovely and beautiful Rachel Patten.

48:43.025 --> 48:44.183
- Shut up.

48:44.183 --> 48:45.747
- Okay.

48:45.747 --> 48:46.580
Anyways.

48:46.580 --> 48:48.450
- This is a really bad idea, by the way.

48:48.450 --> 48:49.460
- You said that part.

48:49.460 --> 48:51.110
Since the radio interview

48:51.110 --> 48:52.770
Darren has not been doing so well.

48:52.770 --> 48:54.770
He has withdrawn even from me

48:54.770 --> 48:58.253
and I don't think he talks
to anybody else, honestly.

48:59.970 --> 49:01.340
He only invites me over now

49:01.340 --> 49:02.980
so I can record random footage

49:02.980 --> 49:04.990
of him researching stuff on his laptop

49:04.990 --> 49:06.800
and, I don't know,

49:06.800 --> 49:08.395
like staring out the window.

49:08.395 --> 49:10.420
- [Rachel] That's a lot of progress.

49:10.420 --> 49:12.760
- Well, at least today he said

49:12.760 --> 49:14.880
that something big was gonna go down.

49:14.880 --> 49:16.128
And I don't think he would hype it up

49:16.128 --> 49:18.067
without something to show for it.

49:18.067 --> 49:22.320
- Something to show for
it as in your death?

49:22.320 --> 49:23.290
From what you've talked about, Greg,

49:23.290 --> 49:26.370
it sounds like he has issues.

49:26.370 --> 49:29.163
Like real, real issues.

49:30.470 --> 49:32.590
- He's kind of out there

49:32.590 --> 49:34.020
and he's a little forward.

49:34.020 --> 49:35.457
- He's kind of out there?

49:35.457 --> 49:36.760
- He's, okay--
- Greg.

49:36.760 --> 49:38.157
- I don't know if he's insane,

49:38.157 --> 49:38.990
if that's what you're getting at.

49:38.990 --> 49:42.010
- You don't know anything about him, Greg.

49:42.010 --> 49:43.720
You don't know where he came from,

49:43.720 --> 49:44.890
about his parents.

49:44.890 --> 49:48.580
You have no idea about anything.

49:48.580 --> 49:51.390
- I know he's not dangerous, okay?

49:51.390 --> 49:52.573
And that's like the
important thing, right?

49:52.573 --> 49:54.773
- I'm not talking about
him being dangerous.

49:55.950 --> 49:57.163
- Then what are you talking about?

49:57.163 --> 49:57.996
- I...

49:59.000 --> 50:01.571
It sounds like you're
taking advantage of him.

50:01.571 --> 50:02.871
- Taking advantage of him?

50:04.620 --> 50:06.738
What, like he's not
taking advantage of me?

50:06.738 --> 50:08.073
- Shut up, Greg.

50:09.138 --> 50:09.971
- Okay.

50:11.370 --> 50:12.393
- If I were you,

50:13.260 --> 50:16.090
I would at least try to figure out

50:17.140 --> 50:18.540
what it is I'm dealing with.

50:20.430 --> 50:22.770
- How would you approach that?

50:22.770 --> 50:24.314
- I don't know, Greg.

50:24.314 --> 50:26.243
You're the one making a documentary.

50:31.593 --> 50:34.392
(Greg sighs)

50:34.392 --> 50:35.946
This is it.

50:35.946 --> 50:37.696
- [Greg] There he is.

50:39.263 --> 50:40.750
- Hey, hey, guys.

50:40.750 --> 50:42.100
Glad you could make it
all the way out here.

50:42.100 --> 50:43.604
- Yeah.
